Privacy Policy

This app respects and protects the privacy of all users. To provide you with more accurate and personalized services, this app will use and disclose your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. However, this app will treat this information with the utmost diligence and prudence. Except as otherwise provided in this Privacy Policy, this app will not disclose or provide this information to any third party without your prior permission.

This app may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. By using this app's services, you are deemed to have agreed to all of this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is an integral part of this app's Service Agreement.

1. Scope of Application

a) When using this app's services, you will authorize the relevant permissions requested by this app.

2. Use of Information

a) After obtaining your access permissions, this app will use these permissions to provide services.

b) This app will not use unauthorized permissions.

3. Disclosure of Information

a) This app will not disclose your information to untrusted third parties.

b) Disclosure to third parties or administrative or judicial bodies in accordance with relevant legal provisions or as required by administrative or judicial bodies;

c) Disclosure to third parties is necessary if you violate relevant national laws, regulations, or this app's service agreement or related rules.

4. Information Storage and Exchange

a) The data generated by this app about you will be stored locally in this app's sandbox and will not be uploaded to any server. Please use it with confidence.

5. Information Security

a) This app's data is stored in this app's sandbox. Please keep it safe on your device.

